d, teaching status, location).{$<$}/p{$><$}/div{$><$}div id="" class="section"{$><$}h3 class="abstractTitle text-title my-1" id="d1756e12"{$>$}Conclusions{$<$}/h3{$><$}p{$>$}Prior investigations have demonstrated a robust volume-outcome relationship for a variety of surgical procedures. However, the present study supports safety of DBS at smaller-volume centers. Prospective studies are required to determine whether low-volume centers and higher-volume centers have similar DBS efficacy, a critical factor in determining whether DBS is comparable between centers.{$<$}/p{$><$}/div{$><$}/section{$>$}},
