ivity to calcium accumulation, permitting a faster rate of calcium-dependent recovery from STD. In conclusion, resistance of \$\$\textbackslash hbox \{PV\}\_\{\textbackslash text\{MS-DBB\}\}\$\$synapses to STD during short gamma bursts enables robust long-range GABAergic transmission from MS-DBB to hippocampus.},
